  • Deprecated Packages 
    Package and Description
    org.cytoscape.app
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
    org.cytoscape.app.swing
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    org.cytoscape.app.CyAppAdapter
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
    org.cytoscape.application.swing.CyHelpBroker
    JavaHelp no longer used in Cytoscape as of 3.4. This interface provides access to the Cytoscape Help Broker and Help Set for managing the JavaHelp system.
    org.cytoscape.app.swing.CySwingAppAdapter
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.DefaultViewEditor
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.DefaultViewPanel
    org.cytoscape.session.events.SessionLoadCancelledListener
    Use SessionLoadedListener instead.
    org.cytoscape.work.swing.TaskStatusPanelFactory 
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.VizMapGUI
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.cytoscape.app.AbstractCyApp
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
    org.cytoscape.app.swing.AbstractCySwingApp
    (As of Cytoscape 3.7) Support for simple apps will be removed in a future version of Cytoscape, please provide an OSGi bundle app instead.
    org.cytoscape.session.events.SessionLoadCancelledEvent
    Just listen to SessionLoadedEvent instead now.

    org.cytoscape.command.AvailableCommands.getArgValue(String, String, String)
    org.cytoscape.application.swing.CyNetworkViewDesktopMgr.getBounds(CyNetworkView)
    This method has been deprecated in version 3.4.
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.DefaultViewEditor.getDefaultView(VisualStyle)
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.VizMapGUI.getDefaultViewEditor()
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.VizMapGUI.getDefaultViewPanel()

    This method has been deprecated in version 3.4.
    org.cytoscape.application.swing.CyHelpBroker.getHelpBroker()
    JavaHelp no longer used in Cytoscape as of 3.4. Returns the HelpBroker.
    org.cytoscape.application.swing.CyHelpBroker.getHelpSet()
    JavaHelp no longer used in Cytoscape as of 3.4. Returns the HelpSet.
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.DefaultViewPanel.getRenderingEngine()
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.util.PropertySheetUtil.isAdvancedMode()
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.util.PropertySheetUtil.isBasic(VisualProperty<?>)
    org.cytoscape.equations.EquationParser.registerFunction(Function)
    Functions registered using this method will work, but will not update properly if the containing bundle is updated. To register a Function, please use CyActivator or CyServiceRegistrar's registerService method to register as a service so updates can be handled properly.
    org.cytoscape.view.presentation.annotations.Annotation.removeAnnotation()
    Use AnnotationManager#removeAnnotation() instead.
    org.cytoscape.application.swing.CyNetworkViewDesktopMgr.setBounds(CyNetworkView, Rectangle)
    This method has been deprecated in version 3.4 and does not do anything anymore.
    org.cytoscape.view.vizmap.gui.util.PropertySheetUtil.setMode(boolean)
